return ['messages'=>['/high-jewellery/'=>'https://eji.com.hk/zh-hans/%e9%ab%98%e7%ba%a7%e7%8f%a0%e5%ae%9d/','<p>A group of butterflies fluttering through a glistening rose garden composing a mid-summer ballet.</p>'=>'<p>一群蝴蝶在熠熠生辉的玫瑰花园中翩翩起舞，谱写了一曲仲夏芭蕾。</p>','<p>A trip to the moon, an elegant 18k gold brooch adorned with La broderie’s hand-embroidered blue butterflies flying towards a dazzling crescent.</p>'=>'<p>来一趟月球之旅。优雅的18K金胸针，与La broderie手工刺绣的蓝色蝴蝶，飞向闪耀新月。</p>','<p>Exquisitely understated, add a subtle touch of elegance and nostalgic glamour with this golden embroidery scarf ring made from 18k gold and sapphire.</p>'=>'<p>精致含蓄，这款由18K金和宝石制成的金色刺绣丝巾环，为您增添一丝优雅与古典魅力。</p>','<p>Fine Jewellery, Lifestyle</p>'=>'<p>高级珠宝, 生活方式</p>','<p>Part of our 30th anniversary project Fine Jewellery, Lifestyle, EJI joined force with embroidery house La broderie to create <em>Ethereal Dream,</em> a collection of hand-embroidered fine jewellery and hair pieces fuse together the craft of jewellery making and an ancient Chinese cultural heritage accentuated by a French flair.</p>'=>'<p>作为EJI三十周年项目的一部分，EJI与刺绣工坊La broderie携手打造 <em>仲夏 • 梦，</em><em> </em>一系列手工刺绣精致珠宝与发饰，融合了珠宝制作工艺与传统中国文化，并由法式风情点缀升华。</p>','<p>Waltzing to their own rhythms, two winged creatures trace an iridescent trail encrusted with precious stones interlacing in the air.</p>'=>'<p>两只蝴蝶在空中交织，随节奏翩翩起舞，留下镶嵌着珍贵宝石的虹彩轨迹。</p>','Blue Butterfly Moon'=>'蓝蝶月光','Etheral dream'=>'仲夏 • 梦','Fine hair piece'=>'精致发饰','Gold Dust'=>'金粉','High Jewellery'=>'高级珠宝','Home'=>'首页','PAPILLON BALLET​'=>'蝴蝶芭蕾','Showcase'=>'珍品展示','Summer Dance'=>'夏日舞曲','editor-text-editor-1a439c7'=>'<p>精致含蓄，这款由18K金和宝石制成的金色刺绣丝巾环，为您增添一丝优雅与古典魅力。</p>','editor-text-editor-40f2ede'=>'<p>一群蝴蝶在熠熠生辉的玫瑰花园中翩翩起舞，谱写了一曲仲夏芭蕾。</p>','editor-text-editor-7d589f6'=>'<p>两只蝴蝶在空中交织，随节奏翩翩起舞，留下镶嵌着珍贵宝石的虹彩轨迹。</p>','editor-text-editor-a29af42'=>'<p>高级珠宝, 生活方式</p>','editor-text-editor-a6b023d'=>'<p>来一趟月球之旅。优雅的18K金胸针，与La broderie手工刺绣的蓝色蝴蝶，飞向闪耀新月。</p>','editor-text-editor-fb6a15c'=>'<p>作为EJI三十周年项目的一部分，EJI与刺